# Visual Design Rules

## TITLES

- MUST be insight-driven
- Format: [Main insight] + (context)

## SUBTITLE

- MUST include time range and metric description

## AXES

- MUST include units
- MUST avoid abbreviations unless standard

## COLORS

- Use max 3 colors:
  - 1 highlight
  - 1–2 secondary
  - rest neutral

- MUST be colorblind-safe

## GRIDLINES

- OPTIONAL
- MUST be light and non-dominant

## LEGEND

- AVOID if direct labeling possible

## LAYOUT

- MUST be clean
- MUST avoid clutter
- MUST prioritize data over decoration